        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>The Wyoming Controversy was a conflict between the governments of Pennsylvania, Connecticut, and Britain, the Continental Congress, and the Indians over land in the Wyoming Valley in Pennsylvania.</p>
        </bioghist>
